{"id":509,"ayahs":[{"number":20,"arabic":"وَيَقُولُ ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ لَوْلَا نُزِّلَتْ سُورَةٌۭ ۖ فَإِذَآ أُنزِلَتْ سُورَةٌۭ مُّحْكَمَةٌۭ وَذُكِرَ فِيهَا ٱلْقِتَالُ ۙ رَأَيْتَ ٱلَّذِينَ فِى قُلُوبِهِم مَّرَضٌۭ يَنظُرُونَ إِلَيْكَ نَظَرَ ٱلْمَغْشِىِّ عَلَيْهِ مِنَ ٱلْمَوْتِ ۖ فَأَوْلَىٰ لَهُمْ","translation":"NOW THOSE who have attained to faith say, “Would that a revelation [allowing us to fight] was bestowed from on high!” But now that a revelation clear in and by itself, mentioning war, has been bestowed from on high, thou canst see those in whose hearts is disease look­ing at thee, [O Muhammad,] with the look of one who is about to faint for fear of death! And yet, far better for them would be","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4565.mp3","surahId":47,"words":[{"id":22464,"position":1,"arabic":"وَيَقُولُ","translation":"এবং বলে","audioUrl":"wbw/047_020_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22465,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/047_020_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22466,"position":3,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوا۟","translation":"ঈমান এনেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/047_020_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22467,"position":4,"arabic":"لَوْلَا","translation":"\"কেন না","audioUrl":"wbw/047_020_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22468,"position":5,"arabic":"نُزِّلَتْ","translation":"নাযিল করা হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/047_020_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22469,"position":6,"arabic":"سُورَةٌۭ ۖ","translation":"একটি সূরাহ (যুদ্ধাদেশ দিয়ে)\"","audioUrl":"wbw/047_020_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22471,"position":7,"arabic":"فَإِذَآ","translation":"অতঃপর যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/047_020_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22472,"position":8,"arabic":"أُنزِلَتْ","translation":"নাযিল করা হলো","audioUrl":"wbw/047_020_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22473,"position":9,"arabic":"سُورَةٌۭ","translation":"একটি সূরাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/047_020_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22474,"positi